{"tid":929661,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人分享一件好Sweet既事","createTime":"2018-12-05T18:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T21:52:29.000Z","uid":139165,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1382d4ea50dba53af473e6f6dede0bc6c6357900","tid":929661,"uid":139165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:19:22.000Z","msg":"最近太多負能量，想聽大家最近有冇發生啲咩好sweet既事，無論愛情、友誼定親情都得。<br />\n快啲散播下正能量比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad53bf1a203db05c291f4ca09b9e16c0d7861b2f","tid":929661,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你好</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ab4d3617110307ffd52551f7facfaaae6eb37a","tid":929661,"uid":142247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:21:57.000Z","msg":"睇番ex送俾我嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609e1e68234359e467651170b18ac25cf78d5c56","tid":929661,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:22:08.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"82f288eeec1678a958b4cff7b9c9f3c8318f69ed","tid":929661,"uid":1348,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:22:54.000Z","msg":"女朋友肯含<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf9f5a576bd41d8c590a96463cfc13fbdf01931","tid":929661,"uid":195975,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:23:23.000Z","msg":"唔想做人 點解自己咁廢<br />\n唔識社交 完全冇朋友<br />\n讀書已經自己好勁 唸住唔溫書都ok<br />\n點知抄到仆街<br />\n聖誕快到 我還是一人<br />\n冇目標冇目的地生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b796b4f0a8ab05730204b6662e9912eff37fe3b","tid":929661,"uid":195975,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:24:12.000Z","msg":"其實可愛&gt;&gt;靚仔<br />\n<br />\n第一 靚仔比可愛主觀 大家心目中嘅可愛都係差唔多 但靚仔就差好遠<br />\n<br />\n第二 靚仔好快睇厭 可愛日日睇都可以鍾意<br />\n<br />\n第三 靚仔容易走樣 講緊短短幾個月 可能肥少少已經keep唔到 可愛就唔同<br />\n<br />\n第四 靚仔好難同人close 可愛比較親民<br />\n<br />\n第五 靚仔比較多挑剔位 例如肌肉 高度 著衫 可愛真係有樣就得"},{"pid":"1ddcb983ecd5413583434b6e53fed917f6de846b","tid":929661,"uid":220695,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:24:31.000Z","msg":"每晚都會打電話俾我講心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n維持左差唔多兩年la"},{"pid":"dabd93ffd4ff0349d082f14dcb8e62921eb04e98","tid":929661,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:24:44.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，到我們的網站&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=zGmyZrjC1OuOnOgxBhMVIb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=caf77537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"8b9e32b49822c9457b1e1e12d86450f3a35f30d5","tid":929661,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:27:17.000Z","msg":"唔好灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 合久必分，分久必合"},{"pid":"8bd4fb2ce4eae727cdaea64f4b8b4f86edb39e5a","tid":929661,"uid":195975,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:28:12.000Z","msg":"做人好辛苦 好辛苦 真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c79af6659eb10a551608ca76249cb102a4b351","tid":929661,"uid":1348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:28:52.000Z","msg":"做女人唔好咁小器<br />\n做男人要有風度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：溫柔的大男人"},{"pid":"4392b122fcbd4a4dc68054281df73c64536ea17d","tid":929661,"uid":431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:29:01.000Z","msg":"It&rsquo;s so sweet knowing that you love me<br />\nThough we don&rsquo;t need to say it to each other,<br />\nSweet knowing that I love you &amp; running my fingers through your hair<br />\nIt&rsquo;s so sweet"},{"pid":"2582932d02a5983f29b8b5fa8f10d090db1d8f6a","tid":929661,"uid":166418,"like":62,"dislike":4,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:36:49.000Z","msg":"話說呢幾個月以嚟同女朋友為咗個死TB嘈交<br />\n嘈到就嚟分手咁濟<br />\n咁就大家唔搵對方冷靜下<br />\n最近我將whatsapp status改做：Will you spend your life together with me？<br />\n結果第日無啦啦睇佢status見到佢寫：yes🥰<br />\n嗰下當堂笑咗出嚟<br />\n同班frd講翻佢都話成件事好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：真人真事"},{"pid":"1a568d2b66197085075b36373ba81da9f9195b72","tid":929661,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:47:30.000Z","msg":"樓主女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15461689feb5a303794120f99068f27a34b1671f","tid":929661,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:49:09.000Z","msg":"你含住我 我亦含住你 太合襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b6575a09632792f5f91d8b37782925a074388b","tid":929661,"uid":34147,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:53:13.000Z","msg":"男朋友寄信畀我，無啦啦加插咗句：平時都係用呢枝筆寫字。嗰陣我都無細心諗佢噏乜。<br />\n後尾傾偈，佢話我應該無發現個秘密。返到屋企即刻拎返封信出嚟睇，諗起佢平時用開擦得甩嘅原子筆寫字，再細心睇原來佢寫咗句Dear Jane 嘅歌詞落去再擦返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61624514cd28b5d554cc51601b6c5368eca8ecf5","tid":929661,"uid":208746,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:54:28.000Z","msg":"有日我要拎櫈爬高痴裝飾，我朋友個女（2歲幾），仲未返幼稚園既，見到我企高，即刻衝過黎捉住我對腳，同我講：「xxx（我名）小心呀，我扶住你，唔好跌親。」<br />\n但我同佢只係2-3個月先見一次既媽媽的朋友，而且個細路女咬字都未正，個下好sweet！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c272539bdc4f9ee4a05fae06614b6730c5f3de21","tid":929661,"uid":139165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad53bf1a203db05c291f4ca09b9e16c0d7861b2f","tid":929661,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你好</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T03:58:54.000Z","msg":"做咩事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af680de84e81cd5400469a8469d81e634386369d","tid":929661,"uid":139165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0ab4d3617110307ffd52551f7facfaaae6eb37a","tid":929661,"uid":142247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:21:57.000Z","msg":"睇番ex送俾我嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T03:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji